{"ID":"20260605141605-q3uw36p","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260605141605-q3uw36p","title":"2023年全国甲卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605142207"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605141618-gpyuw0a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141618-gpyuw0a","updated":"20260605141618"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"临江仙"}]},{"ID":"20260605141618-m4zkqgn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141618-m4zkqgn","updated":"20260605141618"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"晃补之"}]},{"ID":"20260605141618-bawxr3d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141618-bawxr3d","updated":"20260605141618"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"身外闲愁空满眼，就中欢事常稀。明年应赋送君诗。试从今夜数，相会几多时。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141618-ygeqvt2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141618-ygeqvt2","updated":"20260605141618"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"浅酒欲邀谁共劝，深情唯有君知。东溪春近好同归。柳垂江上影，梅谢雪中枝。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141605-e6q6mc6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605141605-e6q6mc6","updated":"20260605141650"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260605141650-9ymjc5g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141650-9ymjc5g","updated":"20260605141629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．下列对这首词的理解和赏析，不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605141650-0opu7br","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141650-0opu7br","updated":"20260605141629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．这首词真实描写了送别的场景，充分地表现出词人对朋友的眷恋之情。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141650-o6wwwpl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141650-o6wwwpl","updated":"20260605141629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．词人时常感到缺乏快乐，而即将到来的离别又会强化这种愁闷的感受。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141650-l3thtsd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141650-l3thtsd","updated":"20260605141629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．因不忍与朋友分别，词人更珍惜当下，数算还剩下多少时日可以相聚。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141650-sx46ifu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141650-sx46ifu","updated":"20260605141629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．春天即将到来，词人希望与朋友同归东溪游览，共同欣赏春日的美景。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141650-hx7o19u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141650-hx7o19u","updated":"20260605141629"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．词的结尾两句被后代评论家称赞为“绝妙”，请简要分析其妙处。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141605-j0y3bzk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605141605-j0y3bzk","updated":"20260605141913"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260605141913-mwite01","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141913-mwite01","updated":"20260605141913"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．A    15．①用动词“垂”“谢”赋予“柳”“梅”动态的美感，运用虚写的手法，想象在春季邀约友人同去东溪岸边，去观赏秀丽的春景。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141913-38gxjpf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605141913-38gxjpf","updated":"20260605141913"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"②此句以春光美景收束全词，通过想象未来再聚之景，表达了对即将再会的期盼，安慰即将远离的友人，更表达出对友人离别的不舍之情和乐观豁达的情愫。"}]},{"ID":"20260605141605-qykqcw3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605141605-qykqcw3","updated":"20260605142207"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260605142002-qy8spes","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142002-qy8spes","updated":"20260605142002"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．本题考查学生对诗歌的综合理解和赏析能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142002-hjx000m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142002-hjx000m","updated":"20260605142002"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“真实描写了送别的场景”错。词中“明年应赋送君诗。试从今夜数，相会几多时”，意思是眼前虽是相聚，明年肯定又要送别你了。从今夜开始细数，到明年分离时还有多少相聚的时候。据此看出词人是明年送别朋友，属于虚写，并不是真实的场景。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142002-1572pzc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142002-1572pzc","updated":"20260605142002"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选A。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142002-l8fhl64","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142002-l8fhl64","updated":"20260605142002"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．本题考查学生鉴赏诗歌炼句的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142002-gsa42xg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142002-gsa42xg","updated":"20260605142002"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“柳垂江上影，梅谢雪中枝”，意思是观赏那江水中倒映的柳影和隐在雪中零落的梅花。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142002-9z49269","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142002-9z49269","updated":"20260605142002"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"词句选取春日的“柳影”和“梅花”作为意象，用动词“垂”“谢”赋予景物动态的美感，写出杨柳的婀娜多姿和梅花绽放后的零落之态。运用虚写的手法，想象在秀丽的春季邀约友人同去东溪岸边，去观赏依依杨柳映在水面的倒影和枝枝梅花在白雪中纷纷零落。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142002-250efif","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142002-250efif","updated":"20260605142002"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"词人通过想象未来再聚之景，表达了对即将再会的期盼，此句以春光美景收束全词，既安慰了即将远离的友人，更表达出对友人离别的不舍之情，将离别的伤感融入一片春光之中，伤感中又带有乐观豁达的情愫。"}]},{"ID":"20260605142207-tser6rb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605142207-tser6rb","updated":"20260605142207"}}]}